<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Trigger>
  <UserStory title="Bank Loan Approval Process: Evaluating Documents and Creditworthiness for Terms">
    <Description>As a bank customer, I want the loan approval process to accurately evaluate my documents and creditworthiness, and provide me with specific terms and conditions for the approved loan, including the loan amount, interest rate, and repayment period.</Description>
    <AcceptanceCriteria>
      <Criterion>The system should review and verify all required documents provided by the applicant, including identification, proof of income, credit history, and employment details.</Criterion>
      <Criterion>The system should accurately assess the applicant's creditworthiness based on their credit score and financial history.</Criterion>
      <Criterion>The system should provide a clear and comprehensive loan approval notification, specifying the approved loan amount, interest rate, and repayment period.</Criterion>
      <Criterion>The loan approval notification should include any additional requirements or conditions that the applicant needs to fulfill before the loan can be disbursed.</Criterion>
      <Criterion>The system should handle any exceptions or errors during the loan approval process and provide appropriate error messages or guidance to resolve the issue.</Criterion>
    </AcceptanceCriteria>
  </UserStory>
</Trigger>